	.string "It doubles the power of moves if\n"
	.string "the POKMON is poisoned, paralyzed,\l"
	.string "or burned.\p"
	.string "It might be able to turn a bad\n"
	.string "situation into an advantage.$"

LittlerootTown_Text_WinonaIntro:
	.string "I am WINONA. I am the LEADER of\n"
	.string "the FORTREE POKMON GYM.\p"
	.string "I have become one with BIRD POKMON\n"
	.string "and have soared the skies\p"
	.string "However grueling the battle, we have\n"
	.string "triumphed with grace\p"
	.string "Witness the elegant choreography\n"
	.string "of BIRD POKMON and I!$"

LittlerootTown_Text_WinonaDefeat:
	.string "Never before have I seen a TRAINER\n"
	.string "command POKMON with more grace\l"
	.string "than I\p"
	.string "In recognition of your prowess,\n"
	.string "I present to you this GYM BADGE.$"

LittlerootTown_Text_ReceivedFeatherBadge:
	.string "{PLAYER} received the FEATHER BADGE\n"
	.string "from WINONA.$"

LittlerootTown_Text_ExplainFeatherBadgeTakeThis:
	.string "With the FEATHER BADGE, all POKMON up\n"
	.string "to LV 70, even those received through\l"
	.string "trades, will obey your every command.\p"
	.string "You will also be able to use\n"
	.string "the HM move FLY outside of battle.\p"
	.string "And this\n"
	.string "This is a gift from me.$"

LittlerootTown_Text_ExplainAerialAce:
